%% ABOUTME: Fix loop retry escalation — same agent retry, fresh agent handoff, function-level fallback
flowchart TD
    FAIL["Validation fails"]
    R1["Retry: same agent\n+ failure report"]
    D1{"Pass?"}
    R2["Fresh agent\n+ failure-category hint\n(not broken output)"]
    D2{"Pass?"}
    R3["Function-by-function\nfallback"]
    D3{"Pass?"}
    ACCEPT(["File accepted"])
    PARTIAL(["Partial result\nor file skipped"])

    FAIL --> R1
    R1 --> D1
    D1 -->|yes| ACCEPT
    D1 -->|no| R2
    R2 --> D2
    D2 -->|yes| ACCEPT
    D2 -->|no| R3
    R3 --> D3
    D3 -->|yes| ACCEPT
    D3 -->|no| PARTIAL
